The '''Starlight Deck''' was the euphemistic name for the lower-class accommodations on the ''[[Star of Empire]]''. Located near the drive chambers, the deck contained no actual viewports. One would have to pass mazelike halls, narrow passageways, tubway, lifts, and moving sidewalks to reach the ship's [[Hangar/Legends|hangar]] or the [[Observation deck/Legends|observation deck]].

[[Kyle Katarn]] was assigned a cubicle-like cabin which featured a [[shower]] and a [[computer terminal]] scanning the ship's layout and activities.

